transcript:

Executive: Yeah sure, no problem.
Executive: Okay, okay, no problem, yeah sure. Mai call from close kar rahi hu, theek hai sir? Okay.
Customer: Ji, ji, ji, okay, okay.
Executive: Okay, thank you. Thank you.
Customer: Yeah, you're welcome. Thank you.
